            <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <div class="about-cont text-white-style">
                        <div class="about-us-title">
                            <h2>Why Choose Us</h2>
                            <p>We provide a seamless platform for managing albums, songs, movies, games, news, trailers, and products.</p>
                        </div>
                        <p>Our user-friendly interface, efficient CRUD operations, and smooth media handling empower users to easily manage their digital content. Whether you want to upload, edit, or organize, we’ve got you covered.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6">
