                        <img src="assets/images/about/01.jpg" alt="About Us">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row about-list-content">
                <div class="col-lg-4">
                    <div class="single-about-area text-white-style">
                        <h4>Our Mission</h4>
                        <p>To simplify digital content management with an intuitive, feature-rich platform that enables users to efficiently handle their media collections.</p>
                        <ul class="about-feature-list">
                            <li><i class="zmdi zmdi-check"></i> Efficient media CRUD operations</li>
                            <li><i class="zmdi zmdi-check"></i> Secure file storage solutions</li>
                            <li><i class="zmdi zmdi-check"></i> Optimized for high performance</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-4">
                    <div class="single-about-area text-white-style">
                        <h4>Our Objective</h4>
                        <p>To offer a seamless experience for users to add, edit, and manage their digital assets efficiently. Our platform supports various media types, making file management smooth and intuitive.</p>
                        <p>We ensure secure storage, fast performance, and a scalable system that grows with your needs.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-4">
                    <div class="single-about-area text-white-style">
                        <h4>Our Achievements</h4>
                        <p>We have successfully built and deployed a complete CRUD system for managing various media categories. Our platform ensures:</p>
                        <ul class="about-feature-list">
                            <li><i class="zmdi zmdi-check"></i> Seamless user authentication</li>
                            <li><i class="zmdi zmdi-check"></i> Real-time content updates</li>
                            <li><i class="zmdi zmdi-check"></i> Scalable and high-performing architecture</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>

        </div>
